output: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> SELECT ?var0 WHERE { wd:Natja Brunckhorst wdt:list of works ?var1 . ?var1 wdt:screenwriter ?var0}
instruction: Write a SPARQL query to answer the following question using the Wikidata knowledge base:

input: Is it true that the cardinality of the group of the Rudvalis group is greater than 1? [SEP] wd:Rudvalis group [SEP] wdt:group cardinality
output: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> ASK WHERE { wd:Rudvalis group wdt:group cardinality ?var0 filter(?var0 > 1.167409152e+11) }
instruction: Write a SPARQL query to answer the following question using the Wikidata knowledge base:

input: What are the jurisdiction which start with the letter v [SEP] wd:jurisdiction [SEP] wdt:instance of
output: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> SELECT DISTINCT ?var1 ?var0 WHERE { ?var1 wdt:instance of wd:jurisdiction . ?var1 rdfs:label ?var0 . FILTER(STRSTARTS(lcase(?var0), 'v')) . FILTER (lang(?var0) = 'en') } LIMIT 25
instruction: Write a SPARQL query to answer the following question using the Wikidata knowledge base:

input: Who did Alfred Kinsey divorce in 1956? [SEP] wd:Alfred Kinsey [SEP]
output: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> SELECT ?var0 WHERE { wd:Alfred Kinsey p:P26 ?var2 . ?var2 ps:P26 ?var0 . ?var2 pq:P582 ?var1 filter(contains(YEAR(?var1),'1956')) }
instruction: Write a SPARQL query to answer the following question using the Wikidata knowledge base:

instruction: Write a SPARQL query to answer the following question using the Wikidata knowledge base:

instruction: Write a SPARQL query to answer the following question using the Wikidata knowledge base:

input: Tell me mixture whose name has the word spiromax in it. [SEP] wd:mixture [SEP] wdt:instance of
output: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> SELECT DISTINCT ?var1 ?var0 WHERE { ?var1 wdt:instance of wd:mixture . ?var1 rdfs:label ?var0 . FILTER(CONTAINS(lcase(?var0), 'spiromax')) . FILTER (lang(?var0) = 'en') } LIMIT 25
